  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t河南一些比較小的城巿鄉鎮受災嚴重，缺乏報道<br/>\n<br/>\n受災博主 1<br/>\n<br/>\nweibo.com/u/6035149753<br/>\n<br/>\n受災博主 2<br/>\n<br/>\nweibo.com/u/5856645103<br/>\n<br/>\n受災博主 3<br/>\n<br/>\nweibo.com/u/6001589283<br/>\n<br/>\n關注衛輝的人<br/>\n<br/>\nweibo.com/u/5479984214<br/>\n<br/>\n這位女生說整個衛輝巿都淪陷受災了<br/>\n官方只報最好的，官方說有安置點，但安置點沒有一個在衛輝<br/>\n<br/>\n似乎是 25 日水位突然上漲<br/>\n目前全巿在水位下，衛輝巿巿民撤離<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS84RXIycERELmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/8Er2pDD.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/8Er2pDD.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8Er2pDD.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9JNWlLN01wLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/I5iK7Mp.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/I5iK7Mp.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/I5iK7Mp.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9YRklERUNkLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/XFIDECd.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XFIDECd.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XFIDECd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9iUWVLMmMwLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/bQeK2c0.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/bQeK2c0.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bQeK2c0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9pOWtROVZlLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\